to do your work well.

00:02:02.400 --> 00:02:04.256
That sounded familiar.

00:02:04.280 --> 00:02:07.976
I started to realize
that I wasn't failing.

00:02:08.000 --> 00:02:10.600
The culture around me was failing me.

00:02:11.920 --> 00:02:13.456
And I wasn't alone.

00:02:13.480 --> 00:02:15.096
